{"type": "article", "id": 41865, "title": "The Body Shop 买家已定，以及，Gosha 和 Burberry 合作款发布 | 浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的新闻。", "date": "2017-06-12T03:15:08Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 1576, "name": "欧莱雅"}, {"id": 7502, "name": "Farfetch"}, {"id": 9472, "name": "Colette"}, {"id": 23444, "name": "The Body Shop"}, {"id": 23871, "name": "Jordan Brand"}, {"id": 37320, "name": "日清杯面"}, {"id": 37797, "name": "Switch"}, {"id": 189, "name": "Burberry"}, {"id": 29151, "name": "Gosha"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 699895, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 29, "image": "img/article/article_show/2017061210524206HtNDlG7n28yaJV.jpg", "contents": "<h3 finallycleanhtml=\"true\" nocleanhtml=\"true\">一些重要的新闻：</h3><p><a href=\"http://www.cpp-luxury.com/loreal-sells-the-body-shop-to-brazils-natura-in-1-1-billion-deal/\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>欧莱雅将以 10 亿欧元的价格向 Natura 出售 The Body Shop</strong></a> | 欧莱雅宣布，已经和巴西化妆品公司、澳洲品牌 Aēsop 的母公司 Natura 进入排他性谈判阶段，Natura 或将以 10 亿欧元的价格买下 The Body Shop。 </p><p><a href=\"http://news.sky.com/story/online-luxury-retailer-farfetch-to-seek-5bn-value-in-us-float-10910936\" rel=\"nofollow\"><strong>英国电商网站 Farfetch 计划在纽约上市</strong></a> | Farfetch 公开发行股票时间预计为 18 个月之后，估值达到 50 亿美元。如果成功上市，Farfetch 会成为英国估值最高的创业公司之一。目前 Farfetch 的投资人包括中国的 IDG、法国的 Eurazeo、伦敦的 Vitruvian Partners 以及康泰纳仕集团。</p><h3>一些值得一看的：</h3><p>法国时尚买手店 colette 庆祝成立 20 周年之际，再度<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/6/colette-dr-martens-special-anniversary-edition-1461\" rel=\"nofollow\">联手 Dr. Martens 带来 1461 鞋款</a>，这双鞋采用了白色皮革鞋面，辅以 colette 标志性的波点细节点缀，风格清爽。<br></p><p>colette x Dr. Martens 全新 1461 鞋款将于 6 月 21 日正式登陆 colette 网店。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612101221h2P3ciSwNnjZgQ6B.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201706121012151mlasjLwFCgyVBZ2.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612101221YjzhW2u4NKZQaIJ0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612101215aF4obwqjPVTthygQ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612101216Qm5tzDKk0sJlGvfd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612101215Nt0LDzBh8nomrUki.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666992\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>俄罗斯当红设计师<a href=\"http://www.highsnobiety.com/2017/06/10/gosha-rubchinskiy-adidas-burberry-spring-summer-2018-collection/\" rel=\"nofollow\"> Gosha Rubchinskiy 在圣彼得堡发布最新系列</a>。这一季，Gosha 与 adidas 的合作更紧密了，足球和复古运动风再次融合。另外，Gosha 还带来了与 Burberry 合作的系列，重塑了 Burberry 经典的格纹图案风衣。据 Burberry 消息，双方联名将于明年 1 月正式发售。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612101132lh2xWg0AT5KfaMOZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612101133BLvMuyDVjoTbZaAm.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201706121011326eEqDM9wNYPlfdy8.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612101133txyEf3XakbBHz4VY.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612101133yEZAWG9sCF8Tx3D4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612101133E8WyICUtnHcmexSk.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612101133BIgXCd6LxUDamMhu.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612101134SuHlWPFgCQqwxi4n.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201706121011360BGZ57AnfWD2E6Ia.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612101136UvPHLsDZ6EwBltdM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612101136DsI1mvqHCKQ9wuN0.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612101136ALvTEjJ4n1isykRq.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612101136ETbOL16hQnjN9pPr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612101155qoKRl2jPsiuypC9N.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201706121017380dJShDPk2LnilyXZ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612101738nNYbQAvtfoT4l82x.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201706121017385xduGPLkWR7V0lI3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612101739stoamHiPEndBSXjM.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612101739YwsGL1WrO9EtF7hU.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201706121017509ezfTuYmrs3bSn4K.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612101856Gz49nDAy5eBROw7Z.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612101911ye2hGdTxFwvH4Si5.jpg\" data-ratio=\"1.500000\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>洛杉矶品牌<a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/6/this-is-ground-nintendo-switch-leather-case\" rel=\"nofollow\"> This is Ground 为任天堂 switch 专门打造了皮革收纳包</a>，除了主机的收纳空间之外，还包括了游戏卡带、充电线等的储藏间隔。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201706121019437PfhjiL1XNpoM5S3.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612101943zpy7MbFNHKgCqlwX.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612101943eiIYxFRfkBXhsUWd.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612101943qyPpMDtdwe8bKlhn.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612101943sEgCqmfXpjVAt1Zr.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612101944ltI8JdQZrxFPKgHO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p><a href=\"https://hypebeast.cn/2017/6/jordan-brand-2017-fall-collection\" rel=\"nofollow\">Jordan Brand 发布 2017 秋季系列</a>。以黑、白两色为主调，带来了 MA-1 外套、Coach Jacket、Tech Fleece 连帽衫以及 Flight Suit 运动套装。该系列将于近期上市。 </p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612104819PbskHYL6eSnw9C2u.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612104819JtQM6sCYAidqFHln.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612104817XJnOfUrRyocG0kMi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612104811Ka2chWZDBiXs5wgA.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612104812J3RtiVa8oBAdjYFT.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612104812jRmOWGXQ0l6Ph3Bi.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/201706121048125OqewrQf3FxptJY6.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612104817a3SzvCbw1QR4E8el.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612104810EV3gbakpqUeCh8LO.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612104810vy1uAWMNzkR4Bb0s.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612104810NGFh0IiLqX3SK6l1.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612104811XPL69Y7HDpiR1N0r.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612104817XW0JOswg1ZkyNUY9.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612104818cXTzodlnMvKLiSAJ.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure><figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <img src=\"img/uploads/20170612104818NJs8DSAHk9nI6Qb4.jpg\" data-ratio=\"0.666875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> </figure></div><p>日清杯面的最新广告 HUNGRY DAYS 还挺好看。它特意找来了《新世纪福音战士》中“绫波丽”的声优林原惠做旁白，以及漫画家洼之内英策，创作了一个以青春为主题，少女漫画风格的视频广告。 </p><p>先来看看 30 秒预告片：</p><div class=\"com-insert-embeds\"> <figure style=\"margin: 0px;\"> <iframe frameborder=\"0